{"tid":23150,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有暗瘡仲化妝","createTime":"2016-12-04T18:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T00:04:50.000Z","uid":43504,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7de8e279bf64c3ed3249ab8d741f48cbadf62f","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"有係絲/巴就算生緊暗瘡仲會化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講吓自己情況：左面豬登有3粒存在左兩個星期<br />\n右邊都有兩粒 下巴同兩個側面都有退 總之照鏡就係覺得皮膚好差 成面都係 因為印+瘡<br />\n<br />\n啲人（老媽子/另一伴）成日叫你花少啲妝啦 點解你唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我鍾意化妝係覺得化妝個人有自信好多 唔化真係鏡都唔敢照<br />\n<br />\n依家用緊：Nars 粉底/Kate 眉粉/RCMA碎粉 簡簡單單<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲分享吓暗瘡用唔會惡化既化妝品？<br />\n<br />\n聽過吓礦物粉底～"},{"pid":"2fdeccf0d876348f84a67661ae934e46ccaedc8b","tid":23150,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:38:05.000Z","msg":"留名睇下男人用咩遮下瘡同印好"},{"pid":"985c90ddb5cb6ad966b734bf170d7c9dca073ecc","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇下男人用咩遮下瘡同印好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗點都有啲貪靚既男人 會想遮遮佢"},{"pid":"a16b69f384cca7575a666750e88412fb2499f8d9","tid":23150,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:49:53.000Z","msg":"礦物粉底<br />\n我用過BM 同Tarte<br />\nBM 支粉底液已經打左入冷宮<br />\n<br />\n其實唔覺得同普通粉底有咩分別<br />\n所以依家都係用返普通開架野算"},{"pid":"65b763426a3ccb3dce5a1316c5c98c80c9dd6df4","tid":23150,"uid":23641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:50:01.000Z","msg":"真心如果無緊要事都日日化妝 暗瘡好唔返都幾抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  生暗瘡最好mask都唔好敷or搽野避開"},{"pid":"6d92fb7d468ee96705982b301be6b6fd972b3e1e","tid":23150,"uid":23641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"Btw試過幾隻覺得maybelline雖然最cheap但好好用"},{"pid":"61184b8d8eda4ede45a25d2f769437a979393f96","tid":23150,"uid":9451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:54:40.000Z","msg":"同樓主情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一轉天氣就係咁爆 <br />\n番工先化 做緊parttime"},{"pid":"0ca130028b3656ecd60132cfcdd2c0332af3ab2c","tid":23150,"uid":4702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:54:55.000Z","msg":"礦物粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用開om同bm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢個天氣用會有少少乾"},{"pid":"b5b9605bf4124d183dc911e16c81e14aa3c21972","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>礦物粉底<br />\n我用過BM 同Tarte<br />\nBM 支粉底液已經打左入冷宮<br />\n<br />\n其實唔覺得同普通粉底有咩分別<br />\n所以依家都係用返普通開架野算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲人話礦物係比較岩爆瘡用架啵 不過好似好乾皮"},{"pid":"ccbaf644f44f34262dff34efa8671b97376802c5","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心如果無緊要事都日日化妝 暗瘡好唔返都幾抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  生暗瘡最好mask都唔好敷or搽野避開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔想理你 完"},{"pid":"d084099a0473a2192eb76c21f93319296d326f29","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一轉天氣就係咁爆 <br />\n番工先化 做緊parttime</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉天氣我唔會特別爆 唔知係咪因爲啲瘡係內分泌失調<br />\n<br />\n絲做咩PT？"},{"pid":"8095e1718a0ea184dcf5129f7fb2ed79d4b24d6a","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>礦物粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用開om同bm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢個天氣用會有少少乾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係格黎POST睇到OM 但唔知係咩黎 因為無個全名<br />\n<br />\n我用NARS呢排會甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6782da1e1d63376f5ea68b5a6483364fcabd67","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"講吓點解唔去格黎POST問<br />\n<br />\n因為暗瘡肌用既人同乾/油好似唔太相同<br />\n<br />\n搵到自己岩既護膚化妝品都要經過好耐時間<br />\n<br />\n講開護膚我用理膚寶水系列（睇下台灣youtuber所以用中譯名） <br />\n<br />\n之前睇過啲文章話暗瘡皮一定一定要用防曬 準備入手個個作者介紹既 舒特膚兒童個款 因為佢介紹啲產品多數係幸福肌 香港好似無得買<br />\n<br />\n大家可以去印呀/護膚/化妝咩都講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117cdf93df49f1702adad3cd45c6946834f7acb8","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"承上 大家有性趣我可以貼個個BLOG出黎 <br />\n佢會講防曬/落妝/定妝/粉底既推薦 不過用過佢介紹蜜蜂爺爺既暗瘡洗面 唔太得<br />\n<br />\n另外我真心建議暗瘡皮絲打唔好用開架韓國cushion真係大伏（唔知專櫃啦）香港太濕熱真係會爆到你驚 韓國天氣乾燥先會岩用氣墊粉底<br />\n<br />\n希望交流吓資訊 呻吓暗瘡煩惱啦 收藏呢個POST搵吓有無咩得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91790ea270649179eda2ea9ebd7675a7b1346605","tid":23150,"uid":4702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>礦物粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用開om同bm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過呢個天氣用會有少少乾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係格黎POST睇到OM 但唔知係咩黎 因為無個全名<br />\n<br />\n我用NARS呢排會甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nom全名only minerals<br />\n真心想護好膚就多d去隔離post爬文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我由幾年前開始追 聽絲打介紹買過唔少正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1d848a7d39aaa9edfd6d7c2082c8544e865ac8","tid":23150,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>礦物粉底<br />\n我用過BM 同Tarte<br />\nBM 支粉底液已經打左入冷宮<br />\n<br />\n其實唔覺得同普通粉底有咩分別<br />\n所以依家都係用返普通開架野算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲人話礦物係比較岩爆瘡用架啵 不過好似好乾皮</blockquote><br />\nTarte 幾好用既，不過厚身<br />\nLM 可能粉狀會好d，但唔知遮瑕度如何<br />\n<br />\n我皮膚都好乾，成日甩皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae6262f42ee2c15e8e7ab4e686e60f52d099dc4","tid":23150,"uid":7779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:24:44.000Z","msg":"之前睇youtube教 要睇化妝品個成份，唔好用含有矽靈、環戊矽氧烷等等，仲有其他 有興趣我至搵番段片，仲有介紹護膚好似幾好。<br />\n<br />\nbtw我都係暗瘡肌，依半年搽左粉底愈搽愈差，毛孔都塞。依排都開始無搽 因為搽開果隻有齊佢講既成份，又更加引起粉刺，所以索性唔搽底 畫下眉等等就算"},{"pid":"63d205a1eb61bfaa52d772776a6b8dc3642a6f0b","tid":23150,"uid":20929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:31:32.000Z","msg":"化就唔知咩牌子好<br />\n不過之前聽我個美座師講<br />\nInxxxx free 嘅痱子mask日日敷<br />\n皮膚真係有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我由爛面變返好<br />\n<br />\n利申非打手"},{"pid":"d2e5d3071a8c0cf62bc77bb4503e88b60e9ab732","tid":23150,"uid":20929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>化就唔知咩牌子好<br />\n不過之前聽我個美<span style=\"color: red;\">容</span>師講<br />\nInxxxx free 嘅痱子mask日日敷<br />\n皮膚真係有改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我由爛面變返好<br />\n<br />\n利申非打手</blockquote>"},{"pid":"078b972808d689d420d961e1aacc2c3bb4c6b2c8","tid":23150,"uid":3098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T19:55:36.000Z","msg":"其實用d話有茶樹 或者消炎作用既遮瑕膏有無幫助<br />\n真係好想遮住粒瘡先出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73808344eef2f905d949fc2d2559b7ec4a9cb0ce","tid":23150,"uid":43504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T20:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實用d話有茶樹 或者消炎作用既遮瑕膏有無幫助<br />\n真係好想遮住粒瘡先出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己用過茶樹成份既遮暇筆 但效果好似粉人咁<br />\n聽講NARS遮暇係不致粉刺 不過我覺得粉底夠遮暇 所以無留意呢方面既產品"},{"pid":"5bc49e9411504d7dc0e822f83ef38c53afaeaf9f","tid":23150,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"😸危殆bb一鍵留名！！"},{"pid":"dd44bf753044aa14aff7b5fcf60a3a4544123805","tid":23150,"uid":5265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"雖然明知化妝會令暗瘡更嚴重 但唔化真係無勇氣見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af84038f6efb82ce1fbcaad0cfa44cc6cc0ac79","tid":23150,"uid":38144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"雖然我係男 唔化妝 但係我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著得樣衰自信都會冇晒"},{"pid":"27ae528e3b815dfb4ffdc04197d3d0cc2a6277fd","tid":23150,"uid":5011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"其實有暗瘡真係唔應該化妝 好惡性循環<br />\n以前壓力大個陣我都爆過一輪，而家有啲印同隔唔中一兩粒，每日都只會用遮暇筆點落啲印同瘡仔度遮下，無瘡既地方係唔會查粉。<br />\n用緊bobbie brown支筆狀定點遮暇霜，有消炎作用，同遮暇度都幾好，唔會令暗瘡惡化，可以試下。"}]}